    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's weird how you used \"proponents of free-market capitalism\" to describe one side, but just said \"some economists\" for the other. it makes it sound like the wage suppression thing is just a niche debate while the growth part is the standard economic view. isnt the impact on wages a pretty massive, well-documented economic reality for most low-income workers?",
